- cs.SD (Software Engineering) is a possibility as the paper proposes a new network embedding framework.
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is a possibility as the paper mentions network mining tasks such as link prediction and social recommendation, which are related to information retrieval.
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a possibility as the paper deals with representing high-dimensional and sparse data in low-dimensional and continuous representations.
